110 // second thread to get transform messages from the OpenIGTL-Interface
111 void Tapi_iiwa::openIGTLinkTransformThread()
112 {
113  ROS_INFO("Entering Transformation Thread");
114  transformSocket_ = igtl::ClientSocket::New();
115  transformSocket_->DebugOff();
116 
117  double startTime = ros::Time::now().toSec();
118  double endTime = ros::Time::now().toSec();
119  do
120  {
121  rTransform = transformSocket_->ConnectToServer(TRANSFORM_IP, TRANSFORM_PORT);
122  endTime = ros::Time::now().toSec();
123  ROS_WARN_NAMED("ROSOpenIGTL", "Trying to connect to OpenIGTL-Server");
124  } while (rTransform == -1 && ros::ok() && endTime - startTime <= CONNECTION_TIMEOUT);
125  if (rTransform == -1)
126  {
127  ROS_ERROR("No OpenIGTLink-Server available");
128  ros::shutdown();
129  }
130 
131  while (rTransform != -1 && ros::ok())
132  {
133  igtl::MessageHeader::Pointer messageHeaderTransform;
134  messageHeaderTransform = igtl::MessageHeader::New();
135  this->receiveTransform(transformSocket_, messageHeaderTransform);
136  rTransform = transformSocket_->GetConnected();
137  }
138  transformSocket_->CloseSocket();
139  ROS_ERROR("No OpenIGTLink-Server available");
140  ros::shutdown();
141 }

143 void Tapi_iiwa::openIGTLinkThread()
144 {
145  ROS_INFO("Entering Command Thread");
146  commandSocket_ = igtl::ClientSocket::New();
147  commandSocket_->DebugOff();
148  rCommand = -10;
149  double startTime = ros::Time::now().toSec();
150  double endTime = ros::Time::now().toSec();
151  ROS_INFO_STREAM("rCommand: " << rCommand);
152  do
153  {
154  rCommand = commandSocket_->ConnectToServer(COMMAND_IP, COMMAND_PORT);
155  endTime = ros::Time::now().toSec();
156  ROS_WARN_NAMED("ROSOpenIGTL", "Trying to connect to OpenIGTL-Server");
157  } while (rCommand == -1 && ros::ok() && endTime - startTime <= CONNECTION_TIMEOUT);
158  if (rCommand == -1)
159  {
160  ROS_ERROR("No OpenIGTLink-Server available");
161  ros::shutdown();
162  }
163 
164  ROS_DEBUG_STREAM("rCommand: " << rCommand << " rTransform: " << rTransform);
165 
166  this->sendCommand(commandSocket_, "Idle;");
167  ros::Rate rate(30);
168  while (rCommand != -1 && ros::ok())
169  {
170  if (sendTransformFlag)
171  {
172  sendTransformFlag = false;
173  igtl::MessageHeader::Pointer messageHeaderCommand;
174  messageHeaderCommand = igtl::MessageHeader::New();
175  positionReached_ = this->positionReached(commandSocket_, messageHeaderCommand);
176  }
177 
178  if (commandReceivedFromROS)
179  {
180  commandStringMutex_.lock();
181  this->sendCommand(commandSocket_, openIGTLCommandString);
182  commandStringMutex_.unlock();
183  transformReceived_ = false;
184  }
185  rCommand = commandSocket_->GetConnected();
186  rate.sleep();
187  }
188  commandSocket_->CloseSocket();
189  ROS_ERROR("No OpenIGTLink-Server available");
190  ros::shutdown();
191 }

193 int Tapi_iiwa::positionReached(igtl::ClientSocket::Pointer &socket, igtl::MessageBase::Pointer &msgHeader)
194 {
195  msgHeader->InitPack();
196  rCommand = socket->Receive(msgHeader->GetPackPointer(), msgHeader->GetPackSize());
197  msgHeader->Unpack();
198  igtl::StringMessage::Pointer stringMsg;
199  stringMsg->SetMessageHeader(msgHeader);
200  stringMsg->AllocatePack();
201  socket->Receive(stringMsg->GetPackBodyPointer(), stringMsg->GetPackBodySize());
202  stringMsg->Unpack();
203  std::string msg = stringMsg->GetString();
204  if (msg == "true")
205  {
206  return 1;
207  }
208  return 0;
209 }

211 int Tapi_iiwa::receiveTransform(igtl::ClientSocket::Pointer &socket, igtl::MessageBase::Pointer &msgHeader)
212 {
213  igtl::Matrix4x4 T_FL;
214  igtl::Matrix4x4 jointAnglesIGTL;
215  igtl::TransformMessage::Pointer transformMsg;
216  msgHeader->InitPack();
217  stateUpdateMutex_.try_lock();
218  rTransform = socket->Receive(msgHeader->GetPackPointer(), msgHeader->GetPackSize());
219  stateUpdateMutex_.unlock();
220  msgHeader->Unpack();
221  transformMsg = igtl::TransformMessage::New();
222  transformMsg->SetMessageHeader(msgHeader);
223  transformMsg->AllocatePack();
224 
225  socket->Receive(transformMsg->GetPackBodyPointer(), transformMsg->GetPackBodySize());
226 
227  transformMsg->Unpack();
228  if (strcmp(transformMsg->GetDeviceName(), "JointData") == 0)
229  {
230  int cnt = 0;
231 
232  // Empfang der Gelenkwinkel vom Visualisierungsinterface bzw. dem Socket
233  transformMsg->GetMatrix(jointAnglesIGTL);
234  jointAngleUpdateMutex_.lock();
235  for (int i = 0; i < 4; i++)
236  {
237  for (int j = 0; j < 3; j++)
238  {
239  jointAngles[cnt] = jointAnglesIGTL[j][i];
240  cnt++;
241  if (cnt == 7)
242  break;
243  }
244  if (cnt == 7)
245  break;
246  }
247  jointAngleUpdateMutex_.unlock();
248  }
249  if (strcmp(transformMsg->GetDeviceName(), "T_EE") == 0)
250  {
251  // ROS_DEBUG("T_EE empfangen");
252 
253  transformMsg->GetMatrix(T_FL);
254  transformUpdateMutex_.lock();
255  poseFL = this->igtlMatrixToRosPose(T_FL);
256  transformUpdateMutex_.unlock();
257  return 1;
258  }
259  return 0;
260 }

262 int Tapi_iiwa::sendCommand(igtl::ClientSocket::Pointer &socket, std::string command)
263 {
264  // if(!commandReceivedFromROS) return -1;
265  igtl::StringMessage::Pointer transformStringMsg;
266  transformStringMsg = igtl::StringMessage::New();
267  std::stringstream transformStream;
268  CMD_UID++;
269  if (this->CMD_UID > 999999999999)
270  this->CMD_UID = 0;
271  transformStream << "CMD_" << CMD_UID;
272  // Set UID
273  transformStringMsg->SetDeviceName(transformStream.str().c_str());
274  transformStream.str(std::string());
275  transformStringMsg->SetString(command);
276  transformStringMsg->Pack();
277  ROS_INFO_STREAM("Send: \n" << command);
278 
279  return socket->Send(transformStringMsg->GetPackPointer(), transformStringMsg->GetPackSize());
280 }

282 std::string Tapi_iiwa::rosPoseToIGTL(geometry_msgs::Pose pose)
283 {
284  std::stringstream sstream;
285  pose.position.x *= MM_TO_M;
286  pose.position.y *= MM_TO_M;
287  pose.position.z *= MM_TO_M;
288  Eigen::Affine3d poseToEigen;
289  tf::poseMsgToEigen(pose, poseToEigen);
290 
291  sstream << poseToEigen.translation().x() << ";";
292  sstream << poseToEigen.translation().y() << ";";
293  sstream << poseToEigen.translation().z() << ";";
294  for (int row = 0; row < 3; row++)
295  {
296  for (int col = 0; col < 3; col++)
297  {
298  sstream << poseToEigen.matrix()(row, col) << ";";
299  }
300  }
301  return sstream.str();
302 }

304 geometry_msgs::Pose Tapi_iiwa::igtlMatrixToRosPose(igtl::Matrix4x4 &igtlMatrix)
305 {
306  geometry_msgs::Pose returnValue;
307  Eigen::Affine3d eigenMatrix;
308  for (int row = 0; row < 4; row++)
309  {
310  for (int col = 0; col < 4; col++)
311  {
312  eigenMatrix.matrix()(row, col) = igtlMatrix[row][col];
313  }
314  }
315  tf::poseEigenToMsg(eigenMatrix, returnValue);
316  returnValue.position.x *= M_TO_MM;
317  returnValue.position.y *= M_TO_MM;
318  returnValue.position.z *= M_TO_MM;
319  return returnValue;
320 }

322 bool Tapi_iiwa::stateService(tapi_iiwa::OpenIGTLStateService::Request &req,
323  tapi_iiwa::OpenIGTLStateService::Response &res)
324 {
325  std::stringstream sstream;
326  stateUpdateMutex_.try_lock();
327  if (rTransform == -1)
328  {
329  res.alive = false;
330  }
331  else
332  {
333  res.alive = true;
334  }
335  stateUpdateMutex_.unlock();
336  // ROS_WARN_STREAM(req.state);
337  stateString = req.state;
338  sstream << stateString;
339 
340  // Checkt ob eine Transformation von ROS angekommen ist, die weitergeleitet werden kann
341  // ROS_INFO_STREAM(stateString);
342  // ROS_INFO_STREAM(rosTransformReceived_);
343  if (rosTransformReceived_ && stateString == "MoveToPose;rob;")
344  {
345  transformUpdateMutex_.lock();
346  sstream << rosPoseToIGTL(poseFL_new);
347  transformUpdateMutex_.unlock();
348  rosTransformReceived_ = false;
349  commandReceivedFromROS = true;
350  }
351  // Checkt den Statestring und ob alle Gelenkwinkel empfangen wurden
352  else if (stateString == "MoveToPose;rob;" && (jointAnglesCalled + 1 >> 7) == 1)
353  {
354  jointAngleUpdateMutex_.lock();
355  for (int i = 0; i < jointAngles_new.rows(); i++)
356  {
357  sstream << jointAngles_new(i) << ";";
358  }
359  jointAngleUpdateMutex_.unlock();
360  jointAnglesCalled = 0;
361  commandReceivedFromROS = true;
362  }
363  else if (stateString == "IDLE;" || stateString == "GravComp;")
364  {
365  commandReceivedFromROS = true;
366  }
367  commandStringMutex_.lock();
368  openIGTLCommandString = sstream.str();
369  commandStringMutex_.unlock();
370  // ROS_WARN_STREAM("Commandstring: " << openIGTLCommandString);
371  transformReceived_ = true;
372  sstream.str(std::string());
373  stateServiceCalled_ = true;
374  return true;
375 }

377 void Tapi_iiwa::lbrJointAngleCallback(const std_msgs::Float64ConstPtr &jointAngle, int number)
378 {
379  jointAngles_new(number) = jointAngle->data;
380 
381  // Es wird geguckt, ob alle Gelenke schon empfangen wurden
382  if (jointAnglesCalled + 1 < 1 << 7)
383  {
384  // Binäre Operation (Bits der Gelenknummern zu 1 gesetzt)
385  jointAnglesCalled += 1 << number;
386  }
387 }
